{"tid":672700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王永平倡單程證配額削半　鼓勵大灣區團聚","createTime":"2018-05-21T08:22:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T09:26:13.000Z","uid":5195,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e27d149c4e694276af22950463a3aad9f4d83836","tid":672700,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:22:33.000Z","msg":"香港房屋問題和粵港澳大灣區發展都是近期熱門議題，前公務員事務局長王永平今在報章專欄上建議，政府可將單程證配額減半至75個，在大灣區某地興建方便家庭團聚的「香港城」，以便騰空土地興建房屋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾在政府工作三十多年的王永平表示，將單程證配額減半至75個，「技術上完成沒問題」。他指輪候公屋時間已由3年等到5年，樓價不斷上升，「大辯論又得個講字」，強調「除了（政府的）決心，看不到（削單程證配額）有甚麼障礙」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n社區組織協會幹事施麗珊表示，現時到內地團聚沒有途徑，而即使限制新移民來港，不等於能解決房屋問題，認為香港房屋問題正正因為政府近十年沒有發展。"},{"pid":"1fd37e9e6fb36eaaac78f29486f2c36ad40c5dd1","tid":672700,"uid":104699,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:30:45.000Z","msg":"落地府先團聚啦屌，無錢無技術1隻都唔撚俾黎"},{"pid":"7b809fb13be3033546901e2f69c217aabf092786","tid":672700,"uid":8048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:31:59.000Z","msg":"哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01448ec36fef04c559440a55808b8f0494c3aa9","tid":672700,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933d9cd203d00697e581d24acdbee26ce1c6bc81","tid":672700,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:33:26.000Z","msg":"要求將堆填區搬上大灣區"},{"pid":"eb74c48c0f034f6f95e28719e98cc1ee8815f549","tid":672700,"uid":81562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:34:21.000Z","msg":"應該所有配額都去晒大灣區 學馬時亨話齋搭高鐵返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c336c2e2720ea44a26c72b7a0552